The paper deals with computer vision and video processing, specifically background subtraction, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed algorithm is based on a fully-convolutional neural network, which suggests that it may also fall under the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves data augmentation techniques, which may also fall under multimedia (cs.MM) or neural networks (cs.NE).
